AMELIA SALTSMAN: What?

00:23:12.326 --> 00:23:14.270
What did you say, Cat?

00:23:14.270 --> 00:23:15.728
AUDIENCE: Steak on top.

00:23:15.728 --> 00:23:17.130
AMELIA SALTSMAN: Steak on top.

00:23:17.130 --> 00:23:18.380
Absolutely.

00:23:23.050 --> 00:23:29.025
But I think a lot of us know how
to cook a steak, but most

00:23:29.025 --> 00:23:32.470
of us have trouble with some
of the vegetables.

