AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:23:33.422 --> 00:23:34.880
AMELIA SALTSMAN: Oh, what
was that laughing?

00:23:34.880 --> 00:23:36.080
What was that?

00:23:36.080 --> 00:23:36.480
Yes?

